%h1.text-primary Hello #{@resource.email}!
%h6.text-muted You requested a link to change your password. You can do this through the link below.
%h6.text-muted= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token)
%h6.text-muted If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.
%h6.text-muted Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.
